  "description": "About the job\n5 days on site (Sydney) \nUp to $180,000 + super + equity \n\n🧬 Work on a brand new, AI-powered product using modern technology 🧬\n\nThis is a Senior Engineering role for a talented Full Stack Developer from a product driven environment, ideally that's had some hands on experience working with AI and ML technologies. \n\nMust have: \n✅ Minimum 5 years of experience working in a product environment \n✅ The ability to work across the Full Stack including TypeScript, NextJS, React and Vercel \n✅ A want to work on site, in the office in Sydney \n✅ Strong communication skills and the ability to work well with a small, start-up team \n\nWhat you'll do: \n✅ Build an AI-powered application end-to-end \n✅ Communicate well with customers & senior leadership \n✅ Design and implement API integrations with 3rd parties \n✅ Build reusable frontend solutions \n✅ Implement AI/ML features in an 'AI-first' product\n\nRun through this checklist to see if you meet the minimum requirements before applying: \n📝 I have built products end-to-end (FE, BE, Integrations, Cloud Infrastructure) \n📝 I am based in Sydney and happy to go to the office every day \n📝 I have 5+ years of experience \n📝 I prefer working in small teams and want to be part of a venture from the early days \n\nReach out at brittany@nuagetg.io with further questions about the tole.",
